      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "他们赶到时，火已经烧完了",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f1_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "颍川一带已经烧成了半边红天。三兄弟赶到时，大仗早打完了，只剩焦营和尸体。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.0,
        "w": 1.0,
        "h": 0.201
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f2",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p05_s1",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p05-page-01-f2",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "另一个英雄先到了",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f2_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "败军还没跑干净，又被一支红旗军马拦腰截住。为首那人叫曹操，像专门来给残局收口的。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.201,
        "w": 0.4984,
        "h": 0.1884
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f3",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p05_s1",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p05-page-01-f3",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "他们又被推回广宗",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f3_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "皇甫嵩只交代了一件事：张梁张宝多半会去投广宗，你们现在就回去助卢植。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.4984,
        "y": 0.201,
        "w": 0.5016,
        "h": 0.1884
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f4",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p05_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p05-page-01-f4",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "槛车里坐的是卢植",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f4_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "回广宗的半路上，一辆槛车迎面而来。车里坐着的，竟是卢植。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.3894,
        "w": 1.0,
        "h": 0.1699
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f5",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p05_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p05-page-01-f5",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "张飞想把这口气砍出去",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f5_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "卢植只是平静说清了原委。张飞听完就要拔刀劫车，刘备却硬把这口气压了下去。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.5592,
        "w": 0.4973,
        "h": 0.1657
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f6",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p05_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p05-page-01-f6",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "刚咽下去，又撞见大败",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f6_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "走了不到两天，山后又是一场大败。三兄弟上高冈一看，追下来的黄巾已经像潮水一样铺满山野。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.4973,
        "y": 0.5592,
        "w": 0.5027,
        "h": 0.1657
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f7",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p05_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p05-page-01-f7",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "刘备先看局，再下手",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f7_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "刘备没有多说，只在冈顶看清了追兵和败军的走向。下一步怎么打，关羽和张飞已经从他的眼神里明白了。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.7249,
        "w": 1.0,
        "h": 0.137
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f8",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p05_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p05-page-01-f8",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "三兄弟把败局撬开了",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f8_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "三兄弟像三把刀一起压进败局，硬把溃军救出一条活路。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f8_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "乱世里的本事，这一刻终于被看见了；可前路，并没有因此变得轻松。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
